briefTitle: Change in Cardiorespiratory Fitness and Breast Cancer Incidence and Mortality
officialTitle: The Association Between Change in Cardiorespiratory Fitness and Breast Cancer Incidence and Mortality
conditions: Cancer of Breast, Cardiorespiratory Fitness, Occupational Health
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Older than 18 years
* Performed at least two health assessment tests

Exclusion Criteria:

* Cancer diagnoses prior to the second health assessment test
* Missing data on any exposure or confounder
